item.title: CVE-2018-5240|2024-08-05T05:33:44.228Z -- symantec%20corporation -- inventory%20plugin%20for%20symantec%20management%20agent
item.description: The Inventory Plugin for Symantec Management Agent prior to 7.6 POST HF7, 8.0 POST HF6, or 8.1 RU7 may be susceptible to a privilege escalation vulnerability, which is a type of issue that allows a user to gain elevated access to resources that are normally protected at lower access levels.
